metadata.name: Planet Autumn
metadata.description:
This planet is created from a photocomposition using 360 image technology, graphics and video. All elements of photography are made by me.

This planet is a part of a collection of 14 poetic and imaginary planets.

If you buy this NFT, you will have as a gift the “Printed” version. It is printed on HR quality Diabond Plexiglas with metal suspension. 2 mm acrylic glass, glossy ultra-HD photo print. Printed by White Wall TIPA World Awards 2021. 60cmx60cm
You must send me address for shipping. Delivery time is one month for Europe more for Worldwide.

You will have 2 options to see your NFT
•	On very high resolution on your Screen
•	By scanning the printed version to access to the AR (augmented reality of the planet). A link is related to the NFT platform. 
In the future anyone how had access to the AR version could see the link to the NFT and his owner.

More information on my social media links, or contact me.
